{"type":null,"faqId":9468,"title":"荣耀X1（7D-501u）7.0 是否支持 WLAN 直连？怎么操作？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>支持。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>您可以参考如下步骤进行设置：</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>1.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>在主屏幕上点击<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=29914\" /></span></span><span><b><span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">设置</span></b><span> &gt; <b>WLAN</b></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>2.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">点击或滑动</span> <b><span>WLAN</span></b><span> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">后的开关至</span> <img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=29916\" /></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，开启</span><span> WLAN</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>3.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">点击</span> <b><span>WLAN </span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">直连</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，同时在需要接受文件的设备上开启</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">直连。荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0<span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">会自动搜索可连接的设备。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>4.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>点击需要共享的设备名称与之建立连接。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=29917\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=29926\" /></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">如果荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">与需要共享文件的设备已连接至同一</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">网络，且均已经开启</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">直连，则二者无需手动建立</span> <span>WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">直连，可以直接共享文件。（其他厂商的设备不一定支持此策略，连接前请确认其他设备是否支持）。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span></span></span>&nbsp;\n</p>","faqTypeId":170,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"39","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-Internet-Data-Sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1396253238000,"seriesProductName":"7D-501u","visitedTimes":179,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"WLAN","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}